        section
          h2 The design process
          blockquote Design for the experience first.
          ul
            li
              | Think about flows, scenarios, and activities
              br
              small Structure and navigation will emerge from connecting these parts
            li
              | Design for the existing ecosystem
              br
              small Understand that people already have web apps they know and use
            li
              | Good design often comes from adapting what others make
              br
              small Make it a point to explore how others have solved the design problems you are working on
