          h2 Page layouts
          br
          h4 Generally, two ways to position elements:
          ol style='margin-bottom: 40px'
            li
              | Absolute positioning
              br
              small Not recommended, but necessary for some situations
            li
              | Relative positioning
              br
              small Allows you to float elements and use z-index
          br
          h4 The "display" property
          pre: code.css
            | display: none;          /* hide elements (zero width & height) */
              display: block;         /* element takes up whole container width */
              display: inline;        /* element only spans its contents */
              display: inline-block;  /* shares behavior of inline & block */
