            h2 Clean, Semantic HTML
            p HTML is the language of "sandwiching content between identifying tags"
            pre
              xmp.code
                | <html>
                    <head>
                      <meta charset="utf-8">
                      <link rel="stylesheet">
                      <script type="text/javascript">
                    </head>

                    <body>
                      <div> Stuff </div>
                    </body>
