          section
            h2 Some HTML tips
            ul
              li
                | HTML5 introduces new tags that help to better identify content:
                  <em>header, nav, section, article, aside, footer, hgroup</em>
              li
                | use <code>[strong]</code> and <code>[em]</code> instead of
                  <code>[b]</code> and <code>[i]</code> tags
              li Avoid table layouts
              li Try to use as little markup as possible
