        section
          section
            h2 Advanced CSS techniques
            br
            h4
              | Let's start with sprites
            ul
              li
                | The problem:
                br
                small Using a lot of images results in too many web requests
              li.fragment
                | The solution:
                br
                small Put them all in one image file and use CSS to slice relevant parts
          section
            h2 Sprites example
            pre
              xmp.html
                | <div class="ui" id="up"></div>

                  <div class="ui" id="down"></div>

                  <div class="ui" id="left"></div>

                  <div class="ui" id="right"></div>
            pre: code.css
              | .ui {
                  width: 40px;
                  height: 40px;
                  float: left;
                  margin: 5px;
                  background: url('img/my_sprite.png'); /* 40 x 160 px image */
                }

                #up { background-position: 0px 0px; }

                #down { background-position: 0px -40px; }

                #left { background-position: 0px -80px; }

                #right { background-position: 0px -120px; }
